        <Parent_String>transitional periods Stone Age to Bronze Age [300106747], three-age system [300106723], styles, periods, and cultures by general era [300111078], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
